<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3588" src="http://www.yempo-solutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/alarm-clock-590383_640.jpg" alt="outsourcing-time-difference" width="640" height="426" />

One of the main issues often faced by overseas companies is the time-difference. This is not an issue in the Philippines. Local employees have very flexible working hours so they can accommodate their clients' needs, regardless of location.
